    "body": "This PR fixed issue #160.\r\n\r\nOn my H800, \r\nbefore fix:\r\n```\r\nTesting GEMM:\r\n > Perf (m=  128, n= 2112, k= 7168, 1D2D, layout=NT, BF16, acc=0): launch   50 us |   13 us |  302 TFLOPS | 1294 GB/s\r\n > Perf (m=  128, n=24576, k= 1536, 1D2D, layout=NT, BF16, acc=0): launch   57 us |   22 us |  443 TFLOPS | 2029 GB/s\r\n > Perf (m=  128, n=32768, k=  512, 1D2D, layout=NT, BF16, acc=0): launch   80 us |   13 us |  338 TFLOPS | 1983 GB/s\r\n > Perf (m=  128, n= 7168, k=16384, 1D2D, layout=NT, BF16, acc=0): launch   52 us |   55 us |  542 TFLOPS | 2190 GB/s\r\n > Perf (m=  128, n= 4096, k= 7168, 1D2D, layout=NT, BF16, acc=0): launch   51 us |   19 us |  399 TFLOPS | 1665 GB/s\r\n > Perf (m=  128, n= 7168, k= 2048, 1D2D, layout=NT, BF16, acc=0): launch   63 us |   11 us |  351 TFLOPS | 1569 GB/s\r\n > Perf (m= 4096, n= 2112, k= 7168, 1D2D, layout=NT, BF16, acc=0): launch   56 us |   96 us | 1296 TFLOPS |  656 GB/s\r\n > Perf (m= 4096, n=24576, k= 1536, 1D2D, layout=NT, BF16, acc=0): launch   61 us |  245 us | 1263 TFLOPS | 1003 GB/s\r\n > Perf (m= 4096, n=32768, k=  512, 1D2D, layout=NT, BF16, acc=0): launch   69 us |  146 us |  938 TFLOPS | 1962 GB/s\r\n > Perf (m= 4096, n= 7168, k=16384, 1D2D, layout=NT, BF16, acc=0): launch   65 us |  648 us | 1484 TFLOPS |  379 GB/s\r\n > Perf (m= 4096, n= 4096, k= 7168, 1D2D, layout=NT, BF16, acc=0): launch   59 us |  169 us | 1424 TFLOPS |  552 GB/s\r\n > Perf (m= 4096, n= 7168, k= 2048, 1D2D, layout=NT, BF16, acc=0): launch   55 us |   97 us | 1237 TFLOPS |  844 GB/s\r\n\r\nTesting m-grouped contiguous GEMM:\r\n > Perf (num_groups=4, m=35456, n= 4096, k= 7168, 1D2D, layout=NT): 2061 us | 1010 TFLOPS |  325 GB/s\r\n > Perf (num_groups=4, m=36096, n= 7168, k= 2048, 1D2D, layout=NT): 1099 us |  964 TFLOPS |  594 GB/s\r\n > Perf (num_groups=8, m=32384, n= 4096, k= 7168, 1D2D, layout=NT): 1921 us |  990 TFLOPS |  385 GB/s\r\n > Perf (num_groups=8, m=31232, n= 7168, k= 2048, 1D2D, layout=NT):  920 us |  996 TFLOPS |  686 GB/s\r\n\r\nTesting m-grouped masked GEMM:\r\n > Perf (num_groups=1, expected_m_per_group=1024, n=4096, k=7168, 1D2D):   80 us |  773 TFLOPS |  574 GB/s\r\n > Perf (num_groups=1, expected_m_per_group=1024, n=7168, k=2048, 1D2D):   45 us |  725 TFLOPS |  729 GB/s\r\n > Perf (num_groups=2, expected_m_per_group= 512, n=4096, k=7168, 1D2D):   92 us |  738 TFLOPS |  833 GB/s\r\n > Perf (num_groups=2, expected_m_per_group= 512, n=7168, k=2048, 1D2D):   44 us |  659 TFLOPS | 1040 GB/s\r\n > Perf (num_groups=4, expected_m_per_group= 256, n=4096, k=7168, 1D2D):   97 us |  669 TFLOPS | 1385 GB/s\r\n > Perf (num_groups=4, expected_m_per_group= 256, n=7168, k=2048, 1D2D):   48 us |  553 TFLOPS | 1531 GB/s\r\n```\r\nafter fix:\r\n```\r\nTesting GEMM:\r\n > Perf (m=  128, n= 2112, k= 7168, 1D2D, layout=NT, BF16, acc=0): launch   51 us |   13 us |  303 TFLOPS | 1300 GB/s\r\n > Perf (m=  128, n=24576, k= 1536, 1D2D, layout=NT, BF16, acc=0): launch   48 us |   22 us |  443 TFLOPS | 2028 GB/s\r\n > Perf (m=  128, n=32768, k=  512, 1D2D, layout=NT, BF16, acc=0): launch   51 us |   13 us |  335 TFLOPS | 1971 GB/s\r\n > Perf (m=  128, n= 7168, k=16384, 1D2D, layout=NT, BF16, acc=0): launch   49 us |   56 us |  541 TFLOPS | 2185 GB/s\r\n > Perf (m=  128, n= 4096, k= 7168, 1D2D, layout=NT, BF16, acc=0): launch   51 us |   19 us |  404 TFLOPS | 1684 GB/s\r\n > Perf (m=  128, n= 7168, k= 2048, 1D2D, layout=NT, BF16, acc=0): launch   57 us |   11 us |  353 TFLOPS | 1578 GB/s\r\n > Perf (m= 4096, n= 2112, k= 7168, 1D2D, layout=NT, BF16, acc=0): launch   51 us |   96 us | 1292 TFLOPS |  653 GB/s\r\n > Perf (m= 4096, n=24576, k= 1536, 1D2D, layout=NT, BF16, acc=0): launch   50 us |  245 us | 1261 TFLOPS | 1002 GB/s\r\n > Perf (m= 4096, n=32768, k=  512, 1D2D, layout=NT, BF16, acc=0): launch   59 us |  146 us |  941 TFLOPS | 1967 GB/s\r\n > Perf (m= 4096, n= 7168, k=16384, 1D2D, layout=NT, BF16, acc=0): launch   53 us |  649 us | 1482 TFLOPS |  378 GB/s\r\n > Perf (m= 4096, n= 4096, k= 7168, 1D2D, layout=NT, BF16, acc=0): launch   49 us |  169 us | 1423 TFLOPS |  551 GB/s\r\n > Perf (m= 4096, n= 7168, k= 2048, 1D2D, layout=NT, BF16, acc=0): launch   47 us |   97 us | 1237 TFLOPS |  844 GB/s\r\n\r\nTesting m-grouped contiguous GEMM:\r\n > Perf (num_groups=4, m=35456, n= 4096, k= 7168, 1D2D, layout=NT): 1490 us | 1397 TFLOPS |  450 GB/s\r\n > Perf (num_groups=4, m=36096, n= 7168, k= 2048, 1D2D, layout=NT):  801 us | 1323 TFLOPS |  815 GB/s\r\n > Perf (num_groups=8, m=32384, n= 4096, k= 7168, 1D2D, layout=NT): 1370 us | 1388 TFLOPS |  540 GB/s\r\n > Perf (num_groups=8, m=31232, n= 7168, k= 2048, 1D2D, layout=NT):  699 us | 1312 TFLOPS |  903 GB/s\r\n\r\nTesting m-grouped masked GEMM:\r\n > Perf (num_groups=1, expected_m_per_group=1024, n=4096, k=7168, 1D2D):   79 us |  775 TFLOPS |  576 GB/s\r\n > Perf (num_groups=1, expected_m_per_group=1024, n=7168, k=2048, 1D2D):   45 us |  726 TFLOPS |  731 GB/s\r\n > Perf (num_groups=2, expected_m_per_group= 512, n=4096, k=7168, 1D2D):   92 us |  740 TFLOPS |  835 GB/s\r\n > Perf (num_groups=2, expected_m_per_group= 512, n=7168, k=2048, 1D2D):   44 us |  659 TFLOPS | 1039 GB/s\r\n > Perf (num_groups=4, expected_m_per_group= 256, n=4096, k=7168, 1D2D):   95 us |  686 TFLOPS | 1421 GB/s\r\n > Perf (num_groups=4, expected_m_per_group= 256, n=7168, k=2048, 1D2D):   47 us |  562 TFLOPS | 1555 GB/s\r\n```",
